Code for:
Wen-Yan Lin, Zhonghang Liu, Siying Liu, “Locally Varying Distance Transform
for Unsupervised Visual Anomaly Detection”. ECCV2022.

To run, download data and change the data path in dataLoader.py
ResNet features can be downloaded at:
http://www.kind-of-works.com/data/resNet.zip
Raw Images can be downloaded at:
http://www.kind-of-works.com/data/raw_images.zip

Have fun!
